00:27:21,520 --> 00:27:22,880
You'll feel better after a good sleep, okay?

586
00:27:22,880 --> 00:27:23,640
Let's go.

587
00:27:24,600 --> 00:27:25,400
Come.

588
00:27:25,400 --> 00:27:26,440
Get some sleep.

589
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:10,240
I found you.

590
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:13,480
I'm not playing with you anymore.

591
00:28:13,480 --> 00:28:14,800
You find me every time.

592
00:28:15,880 --> 00:28:17,280
Then what should we play?

593
00:28:17,640 --> 00:28:18,600
Hao,

594
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:20,460
have you finished your homework?

595
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:24,720
Follow me.

596
00:28:37,360 --> 00:28:39,690
I asked if you've finished your homework.

597
00:28:40,960 --> 00:28:41,760
Hao.

598
00:28:43,360 --> 00:28:44,220
I'm asking you.

599
00:28:45,080 --> 00:28:45,840
Where is he?

600
00:28:47,400 --> 00:28:48,120
This kid,

601
00:28:48,120 --> 00:28:48,980
where did he go?

602
00:28:49,440 --> 00:28:50,400
Hao!

603
00:28:51,240 --> 00:28:52,040
Hao!

604
00:28:53,000 --> 00:28:54,440
Hao!

605
00:28:54,920 --> 00:28:55,640
Hao!

606
00:28:59,960 --> 00:29:00,840
Hao,

607
00:29:00,840 --> 00:29:02,200
where did you go?

608
00:29:02,200 --> 00:29:03,860
Not studying properly again.

609
00:29:05,200 --> 00:29:06,000
Fine.

610
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:08,000
Don't eat later.

611
00:29:28,560 --> 00:29:29,240
Hao!

612
00:29:30,040 --> 00:29:30,640
Hao!

613
00:29:31,040 --> 00:29:32,440
Where are you, Hao?

614
00:29:38,280 --> 00:29:39,320
I know.

615
00:29:39,560 --> 00:29:40,480
You are here.

616
00:29:42,800 --> 00:29:44,000
Not here either.

617
00:29:59,240 --> 00:29:59,840
Chao,

618
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:01,300
what are you doing?

619
00:30:02,480 --> 00:30:03,120
Chao.

620
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:08,210
What's wrong? Are you okay?

621
00:30:11,320 --> 00:30:13,760
It seems Hao left this for you.

622
00:30:14,480 --> 00:30:15,880
Since you are here today,

623
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:17,200
