637
00:32:41,240 --> 00:32:42,720
2021,

638
00:32:42,720 --> 00:32:44,320
November 20.

639
00:32:44,680 --> 00:32:46,160
If the person closest to me

640
00:32:46,160 --> 00:32:47,880
