647
00:33:44,920 --> 00:33:45,480
Shasha!

648
00:33:45,480 --> 00:33:46,440
What are you doing?

649
00:33:46,440 --> 00:33:47,200
Come back!

650
00:33:51,600 --> 00:33:52,400
